WEBVTT

00:04.772 --> 00:09.443
(scanner beeping)

00:09.443 --> 00:11.579
If you have a laptop, put it

00:11.579 --> 00:13.947
in a separate bin.

00:13.947 --> 00:15.683
Take out your cell phones,

00:15.683 --> 00:18.086
bracelets, metal.

00:18.086 --> 00:20.054
If you have a pacemaker,

00:20.054 --> 00:21.189
remove it.

00:21.189 --> 00:22.356
It's a nonstop this time, so

00:22.356 --> 00:23.891
I should be back for dinner.

00:23.891 --> 00:25.559
Yeah.

00:25.559 --> 00:27.561
(echoing) Nervous?

00:27.561 --> 00:30.464
(screaming)

00:30.464 --> 00:32.433
No. No, I, um...

00:32.433 --> 00:33.534
They have body scanners and

00:33.534 --> 00:35.069
they're patting people down and

00:35.069 --> 00:35.769
we have to take our off shoes.

00:35.769 --> 00:37.037
So, it's all very, um,

00:37.037 --> 00:38.306
state-of-the-art, so I'm just

00:38.306 --> 00:40.274
glad they're here to protect us.

00:40.274 --> 00:41.309
Love you.

00:41.309 --> 00:47.115
(texting on phone)

00:47.115 --> 00:48.982
Actually, the TSA doesn't

00:48.982 --> 00:49.917
protect us from terrorist

00:49.917 --> 00:53.954
attacks.

00:53.954 --> 00:55.489
Yeah, I'm not just a stranger,

00:55.489 --> 00:56.257
Phil.

00:56.257 --> 00:58.392
I have a TV show.

00:58.392 --> 00:59.827
And you're on that TV show.

00:59.827 --> 01:00.594
No, thank you.

01:00.594 --> 01:01.962
Hi, I'm Adam Conover.

01:01.962 --> 01:02.796
Hi, Adam.

01:02.796 --> 01:04.332
And this is

01:04.332 --> 01:05.499
"Adam Ruins Everything."

01:05.499 --> 01:06.400
What's happening?

01:06.400 --> 01:08.769
♪♪

