(crackling)

01:11.305 --> 01:12.506
(ding-ding)

01:12.506 --> 01:12.906
(buzzer)

01:12.906 --> 01:13.741
Look, I know the TSA

01:13.741 --> 01:14.308
Closed Captions Provided by

01:14.308 --> 01:14.508
truTV

